//Write a program to find greatest element in an array using pointerâ€¦

int main()
{
    int *p,a[10],n,max,i;
    printf("\n enter N:");
    scanf("%d",&n);
    p=a;
    for(i=0;i<n;i++)
    {
        printf("\n value at a[%d]:",i);
        scanf("%d",(p+i));
    }
    max=*p;
    for(i=1;i<n;i++)
    {
        if(*(p+i)>max)
            max=*(p+i);
    }
    printf("\n greatest=%d",max);
}


Output:

enter N:5
 value at a[0]:4
 value at a[1]:8
 value at a[2]:6
 value at a[3]:2
 value at a[4]:5
 greatest=8

Reference:https://funcodepro.blogspot.com/2018/12/how-to-find-greatest-element-in-array.html
